Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for Graduates have been published by Chhattisgarh State Power Generation Company Limited for Graduate & Diploma Apprentice vacancies in Chhattisgarh. If you are searching for a government job in Chhattisgarh then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Graduate & Diploma Apprentice, from -09-07-2021, and till 31-07-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Chhattisgarh and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about the application fee

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a Graduate & Diploma Apprentice in CSPGCL, your Graduation must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 31-07-2021

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 40 years old. 

CSPGCL Graduate & Diploma Apprentice Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

How to apply for CSPGCL Graduate & Diploma Apprentice Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Graduate & Diploma Apprentice. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of CSPGCL and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by CSPGCL
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
